		<td width=468 background=images/border2o.jpg height=17 style="font-family:arial;font-size:8pt;color:#FFFFFF"><b><a name=0>Welcome to the Promised Land</a></b><small>- posted by Nesuril on Jun, 21 2002</small></td>
